List parameters available in the GridTimeSeries data

Source: R/gts_parameters.R
gts_parameters.Rd

Accesses the available parameters in the GridTimeSeries data and provides a table with the name of parameters, their time resolution, units of measurement and the years of available data.

Usage

gts_parameters()

Value

A table with details the parameters that are available in the GridTimeSeries data. Use the variable names in the table when downloading data.
